{"tid":1514236,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC講六月至今中共嘅宣傳策略","createTime":"2019-08-28T16:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:24:53.000Z","uid":66895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9468e46f523d3ef48154dbd30216cab9f229e8e","tid":1514236,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong protests: Celebrities, big brands and China's media game<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-49428931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49428931&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTIMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=7201b47f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-49428931</a><br />\n<br />\n依篇文幾值得一睇，講中國係反送中運動入面用過嘅宣傳手法，知己知彼。建議撳入去睇，以下係中文嘅超簡略版。<br />\n<br />\n文章入面講六月至今有七個階段，中共用咗唔同嘅宣傳方針：<br />\n1）運動開始時，首先沈默應對<br />\n2）聲言外國勢力介入<br />\n3）形容為正義同邪惡之戰<br />\n4）標籤示威者，包括以四人幫標籤四個民主派人士<br />\n5）宣傳外國人也「愛中國」，反對運動<br />\n6）「女巫搜獵」，迫各大品牌作出道歉並聲言海國<br />\n7）指示中國明星展示支持北京的立場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d7ebaa5ab059000251f28c80738010add210e1dc","tid":1514236,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推上頂，文長但關乎出路麻煩大家耐心閱讀，香港人我地要一齊做<br />\n#Chinazi<br />\n#ProtectOurCountry<br />\n#StandwithHongKong<br />\n#NomadeinChina<br />\n<br />\n大家申請咗Twitter AC未，記得用新email注冊"},{"pid":"dbfba3de5e1966da5a43193711dd5f9aa75e6853","tid":1514236,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f30e7b5663cf65aa6e54d749e72db49f8