=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZOUN8Cca_Lg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">重溫811警暴連環<br />\n⒈蓄意謀殺女救護 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">布袋鉛彈爆眼球</span></strong> 警署內瞄準 致永久失明 面骨碎裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<br />\n⒉多名被捕者<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">移送文錦渡新屋嶺扣留</span></span> 切斷律師援助<br />\n放出後有一傷者出現<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>腦出血</strong></span>、<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各有骨折、斷手、斷背、甚至頸椎移位</span></span>傷勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n⒊地鐡<strong>站內 水平發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣、<br />\n⒋警<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">喬裝示威者 發動衝擊</span></strong>、毆打已受制服示威者、<br />\n⒌普通話<strong>軍人 多處滲透</strong>武統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<br />\n⒍<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一米內行刑 掃射</span></strong>胡椒彈槍、險釀電梯<strong>人踩人</strong>、<br />\n⒎<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">縱容黑幫</span></strong>橫行 毆打記者路人、皮肉剝離 <span style=\"color: green;\">斷筋血肉模糊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n⒏濫暴<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">痛毆 重創被捕者</span></span></strong> 打掉門牙、<br />\n⒐屋村<strong>老人民居範圍 發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣<br />\n１０. 殘害救護員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、<strong>救護舉旗警告</strong> 尖沙咀<strong>阻礙救援</strong> 違反國際人道法 屬嚴重刑事罪行</span> <br />\n１⒈疑插贜竹枝 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">造偽證</span></strong> 誣陷被捕者。"},{"pid":"a00a529f0d3fad3d5aac5d40285846e731e7848b","tid":1514236,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:10:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">破而後立</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFfam93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail